    "body": "I was just able to run a script that had a try catch, so marking this completed. @0xPhaze if you still have this issue we can reopen, just provide steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\npragma solidity ^0.8.13;\r\n\r\nimport \"forge-std/Script.sol\";\r\nimport {Counter} from \"src/Counter.sol\";\r\n\r\ncontract CounterScript is Script {\r\n    function setUp() public {}\r\n\r\n    function run() public {\r\n        vm.startBroadcast();\r\n        Counter counter = new Counter();\r\n        try counter.increment() {\r\n            // I modified increment to always revert\r\n        } catch {\r\n            console.log(\"still worked\"); // this got logged, script was successful\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```",
